Marjorie Deanne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marjorie_Deanne 0 Marjorie Deanne (January 28, 1917 – May 21, 1994) was an American film actress. She appeared in over 25 films between 1938 and 1943. Born Clara Pauline Boughton, modern viewers will recognize Deanne for her appearances in several Three Stooges films such as Violent Is the Word for Curly, Dutiful But Dumb and Matri-Phony. Deanne died in Redwood City, California in 1994. Marjorie_Deanne ( January_28_,_1917 – May_21_,_1994 ) was an_American_film_actress . She appeared in over_25_films between 1938_and_1943 .
